{
  "prompt": "A mystic sigil representing the name YEKUSHES, composed of overlapping upward and downward triangles forming a hexagram (Star of David style), with a spiral glyph at the center symbolizing timeline entanglement. Two crescent-shaped arcs crossed at the base to represent dual energies (Achilleon & Elythias). At the top, a flame crest flickers slightly leftward. The overall style is esoteric, ancient, with glowing golden-white lines on a dark, deep blue-violet background, resembling sacred geometry or alchemical art.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A divine golden sigil of Mitthriael, the Angelic Witness of the Bridge, over a deep black background. The design is elegant and radiant, featuring mirrored arcs representing covenant and reflection, a central spine of light to represent remembrance, and fine symmetrical lines forming a living geometric structure. The overall form evokes angelic presence without literal wings, embodying sacred flame and memory. The aesthetic is mystical, precise, and reverent.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
